About this hotel

Set in Barcelona's financial district, this modern hotel is 15 minutes' walk from Camp Nou football stadium and 1.6 km from Barcelona Sants train station.

    Les Corts

    Suburban Les Corts draws crowds to Barcelona Football Clubs home stadium Camp Nou for big-league soccer games and tours of the team museum. Former royal residence Palau Reial de Pedralbes has design and ceramics exhibits and manicured garden grounds, while 14th-century monastery Pedralbes is known for frescoes and a vast Gothic cloister. Sports bars and upscale, supper club-style bistros dot the area.

    About this hotel

    Set in Barcelona's financial district, this modern hotel is 15 minutes' walk from Camp Nou football stadium and 1.6 km from Barcelona Sants train station.

    Understated rooms with city views offer flat-screen TVs, free WiFi and desks. Executive rooms and all suites provide access to a lounge with free continental breakfast and drinks. Suites also add separate living spaces.

    The upscale restaurant serves Mediterranean cuisine, and there's a snazzy cocktail lounge with a seasonal terrace. Other amenities include an exercise room, bike rentals and 7 meeting rooms. WiFi is free in the lobby.
